layout_mode = 2
text = "BlenderKit add-on for Godot.
1. Make sure BlenderKit-Client is running.
2. Wait until Client connection is confirmed in Status.
3. Choose assets on www.blenderkit.com
4. Click on Get Asset, choose Godot
5. Asset is downloaded into res://blenderkit_assets
"
